      <description>&lt;h2&gt; Maps of Delhi - Transit &lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt; Metro, roads, DTC getting around..&lt;p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;container&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;column&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/maps/metro.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;column&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/maps/traffic.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;a-map-of-dtc-bus-routes&#34;&gt;A map of DTC bus routes&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This map of DTC bus routes was created in the style of a metro map, now taken down on the web I had to do a lot of digging to find it. Created by &lt;cul&gt;Sudipto Ghosh and Shimonti Sinha of Citywise in 2016&lt;/cul&gt;. The project seems to have wrapped up by 2018.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
